<emphasis id="B93699433613D07B56E4FF23FE054BBD" box="[151,318,220,244]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Chrysonotomyia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFD338A03613D07B5736FF23FD214BBD" author="Ashmead, W. H." box="[325,538,220,244]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="225 - 551" refId="ref18238" refString="Ashmead, W. H. (1904) Classification of the chalcid flies of the superfamily Chalcidoidea, with descriptions of new species in the Carnegie Museum, collected in South America by Herbert H. Smith. Memoirs of the Carnegie Museum, 1 (4), 225 - 551. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / p. 234821" type="journal article" year="1904">Ashmead, 1904: 344</bibRefCitation>
